---

üîÆ Overview

LockBox is a ritualized mechanism for freezing GLC tokens ‚Äî not as a technical lock, but as a mythic act of devotion.  
Unlike traditional holding, LockBox transforms time into trust. The duration is determined by VRF ‚Äî PoF‚Äôs digital oracle, ensuring randomness with proof.  
Each LockBox becomes a scene in the myth, a sarcophagus of intent, and a ticket to the Keeper Era.

---

üì¶ Activation Flow

1. Participant selects amount (‚â• 10,000 GLC)  
2. Smart contract triggers VRF ‚Üí random duration from 6 months to 5 years  
3. LockBox is created with fixed duration  
4. Participant chooses its fate:
   - üõ°Ô∏è Send to Fortune Vault (awaiting unlock)
   - üõí List on LockBox Market (resell before unlock)
   - üßø Mint as NFT LockBox (store or trade on Getgems)

---

üßÆ Reward Mechanics

| Parameter             | Value                                         |
|-----------------------|-----------------------------------------------|
| Duration              | 6 months ‚Äì 5 years (via VRF)                  |
| Annual Yield          | 10% APR, proportional to duration             |
| NFT Reward            | Based on duration (see below)                 |
| Karma Score           | +1 per 6 months of freeze                     |
| VRF Modifier          | √ó1.2‚Äì√ó1.5 boost in Transfer Draw              |

