‚öôÔ∏è VRF: Digital Oracle

Verifiable Random Function (VRF) is a cryptographic oracle that determines LockBox duration.  
It guarantees:
- Unpredictability  
- Verifiability  
- Manipulation resistance  
- Ritual fairness

> ‚ÄúYou don‚Äôt choose the time. The time chooses you.‚Äù

---

üßò Philosophy

> LockBox is not a vault. It‚Äôs a sarcophagus of faith.  
> You don‚Äôt just freeze tokens. You freeze intention.  
> And when it opens ‚Äî you don‚Äôt receive profit. You return as a keeper.

